OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Kieran
OL,7,FCarter
OL,9,FThe government has said a public
OL,10,Finquiry will be established into the
OL,11,FBattle of Orgreave - the fifth to be
OL,12,Fannounced in 2025.
OL,14,FThe announcement of this inquiry
OL,15,Fbrings the total number of ongoing
OL,16,Fpublic inquiries to 23, more than at
OL,17,Fany time before.
