OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised by members
OL,7,Fof the public, as well as MPs and
OL,8,Fministers, over the ever-growing
OL,9,Fnumber, cost and length of time they
OL,10,Ftake to complete their work.
OL,12,FSo what do public inquiries achieve,
OL,13,Fand, after this latest announcement,
OL,14,Fis the government too quick to push
OL,15,Fthe inquiry button?
OL,17,FWhat is a public inquiry?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
