OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FPublic inquiries are set up by
OL,7,Fgovernment ministers and aim to
OL,8,Finvestigate "events of major public
OL,9,Fconcern or to consider controversial
OL,10,Fpublic policy issues."
OL,12,FThere are two types of public inquiry,
OL,13,Fstatutory and non-statutory.
OL,15,FStatutory inquiries in the UK are
OL,16,Flaunched under the Inquiries Act 2005
OL,17,Fand have legal powers to compel
OL,18,Fevidence and witness testimony.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
