OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FTypically, they are used for serious
OL,7,Fmatters of public concern and are
OL,8,Foften led by judges.
OL,10,FNon-statutory inquiries have no legal
OL,11,Fpowers and rely on voluntary
OL,12,Fcooperation. They are faster and more
OL,13,Fflexible, but can be less effective if
OL,14,Fkey witnesses refuse to take part.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
