OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FThrough the analysis of documents, as
OL,7,Fwell as evidence and testimony from
OL,8,Frelevant parties, inquiries seek to
OL,9,Festablish a legal record of what
OL,10,Fhappened, who bears responsibility and
OL,11,Fwhat recommendations can be made to
OL,12,Fprevent something similar from
OL,13,Fhappening in the future.
