OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FThere are often widespread calls for
OL,7,Fpublic inquiries in the wake of
OL,8,Fserious events. Many see them as a
OL,9,Fvital tool in seeking answers and
OL,10,Fbringing all responsible parties
OL,11,Ftogether in one investigation.
OL,13,FResponding to calls to reform the
OL,14,Fsystem, the government claimed recent
OL,15,Fpublic inquiries have been "considered
OL,16,Fto be an independent, legitimate and
OL,17,Ftrusted method of investigating
OL,18,Fcomplex issues of deep public concern.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
