OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,F"They have shown to be a way to shed
OL,7,Flight on injustices of the past,
OL,8,Fprovide a means for victims and
OL,9,Fsurvivors to finally have their voices
OL,10,Fheard, and to help rebuild trust in
OL,11,Fnational institutions."
OL,13,FBut cabinet minister Nick Thomas-
OL,14,FSymonds acknowledged "there is serious
OL,15,Fand growing criticism of their cost,
OL,16,Fduration, and effectiveness."
OL,18,FThe government claims that, in the
OL,19,Ffinancial year 2023/24, the cost to
OL,20,Fthe public of ongoing inquiries
OL,21,Ftotalled more than #130 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
