OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FStatutory inquiries that produced
OL,7,Ftheir final report in the last five
OL,8,Fyears took, on average, nearly five
OL,9,Fyears to do so.
OL,11,FHow many public inquiries are there?
OL,13,FWith the announcement of the public
OL,14,Finquiry into the Battle of Ogreave,
OL,15,Fthe UK now has 23 ongoing statutory
OL,16,Finquiries, including the Infected
OL,17,FBlood Inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
