OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FAccording to the Institute for
OL,7,FGovernment (IfG), since 1997, there
OL,8,Fhave never been fewer than five public
OL,9,Finquiries running at any one time.
OL,11,FThree of the 23 - the Orgreave
OL,12,FInquiry, the Independent Commission on
OL,13,FGrooming Gangs and the Finucane
OL,14,FInquiry - have been announced, but are
OL,15,Fyet to begin.
OL,17,FThe IfG claims that between 1990 and
OL,18,F2025, 90 public inquiries have been
OL,19,Flaunched ` compared with only 19 in
OL,20,Fthe 30 years prior.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
