OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FWhilst public inquiries vary greatly
OL,7,Fin length, the shortest ever recorded
OL,8,Fwas less than a year.
OL,10,FThe Hammond Inquiry ran from September
OL,11,F2006 to June 2007, investigating
OL,12,Fallegations of corruption by Peter
OL,13,FMandelson over the handling of two
OL,14,Fforeign brothers' UK passport
OL,15,Fapplications.
OL,17,FCurrently, the longest recorded
OL,18,Finquiry was into Hyponatraemia-related
OL,19,Fdeaths, which took over 13 years to
OL,20,Fcomplete.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
