OL,12,FCould things change?
OL,14,FIn 2014, the House of Lords reviewed
OL,15,Fthe public inquiry process and made 33
OL,16,Frecommendations to reform it.
OL,18,FThe coalition Conservative and Liberal-
OL,19,FDemocrat government at the time
OL,20,Faccepted 19 of these, but failed to
OL,21,Fimplement a single one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
