OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FReporting again in 2024, the Lords'
OL,7,FStatutory Inquiry Committee reiterated
OL,8,Fmany of these recommendations but
OL,9,Fdisagreed with the 2014 suggestion
OL,10,Fthat all new inquiries should be
OL,11,Festablished as statutory.
OL,13,FIt concluded there were several
OL,14,Fbenefits to non-statutory inquiries,
OL,15,Fparticularly the ability for victims
OL,16,Fto address the chair directly, rather
OL,17,Fthan through legal counsel as required
OL,18,Fby statute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
