OL,3,CWhat are public inquiries and how many
OL,4,Care ongoing?
OL,6,FThe current government has accepted
OL,7,Fthe latest report's findings and
OL,8,Fagreed that the inquiry process needs
OL,9,Fto be improved.
OL,11,FIt confirmed its intention is "to
OL,12,Fbuild on this important work with a
OL,13,Fwider review of the policy and
OL,14,Foperational framework around public
OL,15,Finquiries," promising a further update
OL,16,Fto parliament in due course.
